{
  "stem": "25027.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I started working with this Jewish woman who was part of the United Nations.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you remember her name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With a coincidence, her name was the same as the doctor's name-- Mrs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Levine, and she was from New York City.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] She spoke Yiddish, also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't speak any English at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- as we were talking, you know, and all that stuff, she says to me, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Jack, you have any relatives anywhere?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told her, yes, my mother has three sisters in America, and my father had four brothers in America-- Zeichners.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] She says well, let's see what we can do for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But then I remembered I had the telegram from the man in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had the letter from Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Weiss in Fort Hamilton Parkway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I said to her, you know, I remember one name of my aunt, a Mrs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Bretholtz that lived in the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] She took all that down, and I says, Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Weiss-- Mr. and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Weiss-- he's also my uncle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I lied a little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] She says, no problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And also I remembered, my grandfather, before he died, he used to be an agent for an American company, selling tickets for people to go to America.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And before the war, he bought four tickets, before he died, for our family to go to the States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the war started, and that was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] She started looking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She took me down to the American Consul.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I have the original paper they gave me from the American Consul, who I am.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
